<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 01:06:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>高管表示，中国公司看好古巴太阳能发电</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-company-bullish-cuban-solar-drive-executive-says-2024-11-04/</link><description>向古巴销售太阳能技术的杭州多佳科技公司称，古巴大力发展太阳能发电的计划对两国来说是双赢，并大力宣传中国的制造业实力和古巴阳光明媚的气候。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 22:43:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinese-company-bullish-cuban-solar-drive-executive-says-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国大选前令人毛骨悚然的平静，澳洲联储设定利率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-pix-graphic-2024-11-04/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 21:55:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-pix-graphic-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>米特罗维奇帮助阿尔希拉尔在冠军联赛中保持完美，但内马尔受伤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/mitrovic-helps-al-hilal-stay-perfect-champions-league-neymar-injured-2024-11-04/</link><description>阿尔希拉尔队的亚历山大·米特罗维奇在周一的亚洲冠军联赛精英赛中上演帽子戏法，以 3-0 战胜伊朗队的埃斯特格拉尔，尽管沙特队的夜晚因内马尔的受伤而变得糟糕。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 21:55:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/mitrovic-helps-al-hilal-stay-perfect-champions-league-neymar-injured-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>Shein 的欧洲实体报告 2023 年销售额增长 68%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sheins-european-entity-reports-68-sales-growth-2023-2024-11-04/</link><description>根据周一公布的年度业绩，Shein 旗下在爱尔兰注册的实体 Infinite Styles Ecommerce Co 的销售额在 2023 年增长了 68%，达到 76.84 亿欧元（83.6 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 18:23:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sheins-european-entity-reports-68-sales-growth-2023-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>美国指责俄罗斯和中国在联合国保护朝鲜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-russia-china-shamelessly-protects-emboldens-north-korea-2024-11-04/</link><description>美国周一在联合国安理会谴责俄罗斯和中国“无耻地保护”朝鲜，并鼓励朝鲜进一步违反联合国制裁，平壤承诺加速建设其“核力量”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 17:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-says-russia-china-shamelessly-protects-emboldens-north-korea-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>头号种子萨巴伦卡战胜保利尼晋级WTA年终总决赛半强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-battles-past-rybakina-wta-finals-2024-11-04/</link><description>周一，世界排名第一的萨巴伦卡以 6-3 7-5 击败意大利四号种子茉莉花·保利尼，在 WTA 年终总决赛中保持不败，进入 WTA 年终总决赛半决赛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:58:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/zheng-battles-past-rybakina-wta-finals-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>英国立法者可能会在明年初就工人权利问题向谢因提出质疑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-lawmakers-could-question-shein-over-workers-rights-early-next-year-2024-11-04/</link><description>议会委员会负责人表示，英国立法者最早可能在一月份在伦敦上市之前就工人权利问题向在线快时尚集团 Shein 的高管提出质疑。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 16:31:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-lawmakers-could-question-shein-over-workers-rights-early-next-year-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟官员表示，中国电动汽车价格协议需要与关税一样有效</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-price-deal-needs-be-effective-tariffs-says-eu-official-2024-11-04/</link><description>这位未来的欧盟贸易负责人周一表示，与中国生产商就电动汽车最低价格达成的任何协议都需要像欧盟上周征收的关税一样有效和可执行。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 15:26:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-price-deal-needs-be-effective-tariffs-says-eu-official-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国国内旅游需求低迷，万豪下调2024年盈利预测</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/marriott-lowers-2024-profit-forecast-us-china-domestic-tourism-drags-2024-11-04/</link><description>由于中国国内旅游疲软盖过了强劲的团体和国际需求，万豪国际集团周一下调了年度利润预期，导致其股价在早盘交易中下跌 2%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 12:12:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/marriott-lowers-2024-profit-forecast-us-china-domestic-tourism-drags-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普的关税将重新调整贸易流动、提高成本并招致报复</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/trumps-tariffs-would-reorder-trade-flows-raise-costs-draw-retaliation-2024-11-04/</link><description>农业团体担心巴西和阿根廷的出口市场遭受损失。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 11:11:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/trumps-tariffs-would-reorder-trade-flows-raise-costs-draw-retaliation-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国石化与TotalEnergies签署为期15年的液化天然气交易协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-sinopec-signs-agreement-15-yr-lng-deal-with-totalenergies-2024-11-04/</link><description>中国国有石油天然气巨头中石化周一表示，已签署协议，从 2028 年开始，为期 15 年，每年从 TotalEnergies 购买 200 万吨液化天然气。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 10:30:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-sinopec-signs-agreement-15-yr-lng-deal-with-totalenergies-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>商务部表示，中国将就欧盟电动汽车最终裁决向世贸组织提起诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-file-lawsuit-with-wto-against-eus-final-ev-ruling-commerce-ministry-says-2024-11-04/</link><description>中国商务部周一表示，决定就欧盟对中国产电动汽车的最终反补贴措施向世贸组织提起诉讼。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 10:29:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-file-lawsuit-with-wto-against-eus-final-ev-ruling-commerce-ministry-says-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉 10 月份中国制造电动汽车销量同比下降 5.3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-oct-china-made-ev-sales-fall-53-yy-2024-11-04/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周一的数据显示，美国汽车制造商特斯拉10月份销售了68,280辆中国制造的电动汽车，同比下降5.3%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 09:36:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-oct-china-made-ev-sales-fall-53-yy-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，马来西亚向越南抱怨南海珊瑚礁扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-complains-vietnam-over-south-china-sea-reef-expansion-sources-say-2024-11-04/</link><description>两名官员告诉路透社，马来西亚已就越南涉嫌扩张南海珊瑚礁向越南发出投诉信，两国均声称拥有该珊瑚礁，这是罕见的不涉及中国的双边升级。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 08:53:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-complains-vietnam-over-south-china-sea-reef-expansion-sources-say-2024-11-04/</guid></item><item><title>沃尔沃汽车10月销量同比增长3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-october-sales-rise-3-year-on-year-2024-11-04/</link><description>总部位于瑞典的汽车制造商沃尔沃汽车周一表示，10 月份沃尔沃汽车销量同比增长 3%，达到 61,686 辆，这主要得益于全电动和插电式混合动力车型在欧洲销量的增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Nov 2024 08:06:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volvo-cars-october-sales-rise-3-year-on-year-2024-11-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>